OL,3,C#1,000 reward offered to crack case of
OL,4,Cman found dead at home
OL,6,FDetectives investigating the
OL,7,F"unexplained" death of a man whose
OL,8,Fbody was found in a house are offering
OL,9,Fa #1,000 reward for information.
OL,11,FAdam Bailey, who was 49, was found
OL,12,Fdead at a house on Tamer Road, , on 16
OL,13,FFebruary.
OL,15,FA 34-year-old man and two 16-year-old
OL,16,Fboys who were arrested on suspicion of
OL,17,Fmurder have been released on bail.
OL,19,FLincolnshire Police have made several
OL,20,Fappeals to establish Mr Bailey's last
OL,21,Fmovements.
